Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔敏  幸好我是你心目中的好人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,暂且算你赌赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我的赌局现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.60,0:00:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经找到有可能是女巨人的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,亚妮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:25.01,Pic,,0,0,0,,{\pos(425,220)}慈悲\N{\fs18}───史托黑斯区突袭②───
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔文他们那帮混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,居然让我们等这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,再等下去来接你的宪兵团就要先到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,估计他们是半天憋不出个方案来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,正在那发愁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,士官长你今天很健谈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来就很健谈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是我当时做出了错误的选择…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会招致这种事态…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道结果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经找到有可能是女巨人的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我们一定要抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,计划将于后天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,地点就定在我们被召入王都时要经过的史托黑斯区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这将是我们最初也是最后的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果失去这次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那艾连就会被交到王都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,追查那群企图破坏墙壁的人也会变得困难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,更甚的是  人类将会离灭亡更进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要将一切都赌在这次的计划上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,计划是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在经过史托黑斯区时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连作为诱饵  将目标引诱至这个地下通道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,只要把她引到最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到那里的大小和强度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就算目标变成巨人  那里也足以封住她的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果发生意外  目标在此之前变身巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连  到时就要靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那么那个关键目标确定就在史托黑斯区吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  目标是宪兵团的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,宪兵团？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这是阿尔敏推断出的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说女巨人可能就是杀了那两名被活捉的巨人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,并且是你们第104期训练兵团的同期生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,请…请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,104期是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那名可能是女巨人的女性的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,亚妮·雷恩哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,糟…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶  那枚戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的谎言果然早就被她看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她早发现我们在埋伏她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,当时应该还有其他办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,反省过会儿在说  先告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我们该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先和三班汇合回到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,之后就按照二次捕捉计划行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:05:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,和亚妮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,和女巨人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连按计划变成巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,协助我们捕捉女巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是三班的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,首次捕捉失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快转到下一个作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,踩穿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,得去救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连  退下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,等…喂  三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,女巨人那家伙  难道不怕踩死艾连吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她赌了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她赌艾连不会被踩死  开出了这个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但这下可不好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,亚妮为夺取艾连已经豁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办  退路被堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我们想用立体机动迅速逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,出去的瞬间也会被她瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直待在这里不知何时就会被踩扁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那时挡住大炮那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,别离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,又变不成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,偏偏在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶  好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:08:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没有明确目的的话好像就没法变成巨人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再在脑中想像一下  用力想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想了  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,确定不是还在为该不该和亚妮战斗而犹豫不决？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,难道事到如今你还认为亚妮是女巨人只是错觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才看到的都是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,杀掉我们那些同伴的不正是那个女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你还要否认吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啰嗦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是正在努力吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,亚妮是女巨人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么认为  阿尔敏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,女巨人最初就知道艾连的长相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她对只有我们同期生才知道的艾连的外号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,「赶着去投胎的混蛋」做出了反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,最大的原因是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为杀掉索尼和宾这两个实验体的人是亚妮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因为杀掉那两名巨人需要高超的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她肯定用的是自己惯用的立体机动装置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  所以当时不是进行了装备检查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,亚妮是清白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那时亚妮交上去的是马可的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她才逃过了审查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会冒出马可来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是你看错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我确实有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那些我已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没别的证据了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得亚妮长得和女巨人很像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就凭那点证据…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说虽然没证据  但还是要动手对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没证据？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要动手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是亚妮怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是亚妮  那她的嫌疑就会被消除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真是那样  对亚妮来说确实不公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是就因为这样而无所行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连只会成为中央那帮家伙的活祭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怀疑亚妮太不妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连  当你听到巨人是亚妮时有没有想到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你和女巨人进行过搏斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你会没看到亚妮独特的格斗术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,女巨人其实就是亚妮这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就必须跟她战斗对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么特殊的感情在阻挠你？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想出了一个计策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我和三笠分别从那个洞和进来的入口同时出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话亚妮她就只能对付一边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,然后艾连就趁机从亚妮不在的那个出口逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那样你们肯定有一个会死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里待着我们3人都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,三笠  准备就位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了  我去前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔敏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你们能和她战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是无可奈何的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这个世界是残酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:49.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0\c&H26706F&\fs45\fscx1000\pos(740.014,0.223)}▇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:49.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord0}目前可以公开的情报\N\N{\r\fs20}席纳之墙①\N作为首都，席纳之墙内约有20万居民\N原则上是作为王室人员的居住区\N因此居民需要特别的市民权
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:54.01,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0\c&H26706F&\fs45\fscx1000\pos(110.196,0.001)}▇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:54.01,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0}目前可以公开的情报\N\N{\r\fs20}席纳之墙②\N在驻扎兵团或调查兵团立下功绩可以获得市民权\N这是贫苦之人能安居在此的唯一方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亚妮  我不会把艾连交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连  马上救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,别让女巨人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一起上  不能让她通过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,护卫小队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,先别管这里  去看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是刚才那个类似爆炸的响声还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,奈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快派出所有兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这种情况应视为巨人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么  这可是席纳之墙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会有巨人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  不准动！叶卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,变装游戏已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别再用那个名字叫我了  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,团长  我也要出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,装备去第四小队领取
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,气势不错  可千万别死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔文  那究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,团长  您的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  艾尔文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,能动的人都跟着我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,与捕获女巨人小队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,艾尔文  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的所为明显是在反抗王政
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,奈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脑袋像鹌鹑公主一样空空如也吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看你的样子还没搞清楚状况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,解除装备  艾尔文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,巨人  巨人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  那是巨人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  活得真悠哉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我原本也应该跟他们一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么会变成现在这样呢  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别妄想解决她  牵制住就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  她对立体机动的动作了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不会这么轻易就结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,回话啊  艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,让
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连被压在石头下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,按作战计划他不是早应该变成巨人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没变成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可能女巨人的真身是亚妮的事实困扰着他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,总之要先救他出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,让  快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没变成功？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连你开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前说过要拜托你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把世界  把人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至是自己的性命都托付给了你  而这就是你给我们的回报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,马可  马可他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  得先想办法解决那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前也跟让说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,人若不能有所舍弃  就无法改变现状
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,若有必要成为凌驾于怪物的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那么他连人性都能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,亚妮她肯定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道她目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  能做到这点就能赢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,亚妮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你这次总该杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不然「赌局才刚刚开始」这种死不认输的话就说不出口了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔敏  来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,来了  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,分队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,您的眼神  太飘忽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为用不着第三方案  预料之外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是艾尔文团长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子  老实一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里你就不能像上次那样召唤大群巨人来吃掉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这次换我来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,将你身上的情报「吃」得干干净净
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,挣脱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,果然陷阱数量太少了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别让她逃了  追！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,人若不能有所舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就无法改变现状
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我那时太过依赖于同伴的羁绊而失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,赶出这个世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不  赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没时间去考虑是否正确
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,总之给我动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别用漂亮话来搪塞过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界是残酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这次又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,艾连
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,把巨人全部赶出这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那一天  心中的愤怒迫使年幼的艾连立下这份誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.82,0:24:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,驱使着他摧毁这个世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.98,0:24:06.97,Pic,,0,0,0,,{\pos(425,220)}城墙\N{\fs18}───史托黑斯区突袭③───
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:54.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur3\fad(100,100)\fn微软雅黑\fs30}Wohlan Freund! Jetzt hier ist ein Sieg.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:57.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur3\fad(100,100)\fn微软雅黑\fs30}Dies ist der erste Gloria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:58.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur3\fad(100,100)\fn微软雅黑\fs30}O mein Freund!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:04.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur3\fad(100,100)\fn微软雅黑\fs30}Feiern wir dieser Sieg für der nächsten Kampf!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:23.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}「無意味な死であった」と…言わせない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:30.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}最後の《一矢》になるまで……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:32.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur3\fad(100,100)\fn微软雅黑\fs30}Der feind ist grausam… Wir bringen…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:35.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur3\fad(100,100)\fn微软雅黑\fs30}Der feind ist riesig…Wir springen…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:41.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}両手には《鋼刃》　唄うのは《凱歌》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:45.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}背中には《自由の翼》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:53.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}握り締めた決意を左胸に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:57.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}斬り裂くのは《愚行の螺旋》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:05.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}蒼穹を舞う――自由の翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:54.54,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}来吧战友！ 这是一场胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:57.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}亦是初尝的光荣胜果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:58.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}吾之战友啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:04.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}为了下一场胜利  举杯欢庆吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:23.94,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}世上不存在「毫无价值的牺牲」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:30.44,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}即便只剩孤身一人亦在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:32.24,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}敌人如此残酷  我们将其扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:35.32,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}敌人如此巨大  我们将其粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:41.16,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}双手紧握《钢刃》心中高奏《凯歌》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:45.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}身后飘舞《自由之翼》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:53.32,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}将坚定的信念置于胸前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:57.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}斩断一切《愚昧螺旋》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:05.86,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}愿自由之翼翱翔于苍穹
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:41.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}例えば俺が俺じゃないとして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:46.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}お前はお前だと言いきれるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:51.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}砂の器を壊してこぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:56.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}心を拾って集められるか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:23:06.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}誰かの呼ぶ声が耳鳴に変わった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:11.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}時が止まったみたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:14.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}さあ　目を覚ませ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:18.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}深い闇を俺は抜け出した
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:24.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}疾風みたいに逃げ出した
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:28.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}生きた屍みたいだった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:35.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}俺達は壁の外へまた会おうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:40.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}地図にない場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:41.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}如果说我不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:46.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}那么你能确定你就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:51.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}破裂器皿  细沙不断洒落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:56.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}心如碎屑  试问如何聚拢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:23:06.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}未名呼唤  化作阵阵耳鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:11.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}似乎连时间都为之停止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:14.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}来吧  苏醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:18.92,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}我逃出了深邃的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:24.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}快得犹如一阵疾风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:28.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}告别行尸走肉般的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.08,0:23:35.98,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}我们在墙外再会吧
